# Simple Shortcode Service

## Create a new redirect

### Command
```bash
curl -X POST \
  --data '{ "redirect": "<%=appVars.website%>", "status": 301 }' \
  <%= appVars.root %>/
```

### Output
```json
{ "redirect": "<%=appVars.website%>", "status": 301, "shortcode": "jkby" }
```

## Use a redirect 

### Command(s)
```bash
curl -X POST <%= appVars.root %>/jkby
curl -X GET <%= appVars.root %>/jkby
curl -X PUT <%= appVars.root %>/jkby
curl -X PATCH <%= appVars.root %>/jkby
```

### Output
```
Permanent Redirect to <%=appVars.website%>
[link](https://www.google.com)
```


